      <title>中国缓慢复苏给奢侈品行业前景蒙上阴影</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/luxury-sector-outlook-clouded-by-chinas-slow-recovery-2024-04-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲大型奢侈品牌的最新销售数据并不能让人相信中国对高端时尚的需求正在复苏，这给该行业的前景蒙上了一层阴影。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/luxury-sector-outlook-clouded-by-chinas-slow-recovery-2024-04-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 15:54:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TikTok首席执行官预计将击败美国禁令：“我们哪儿也不去”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktok-ceo-expects-defeat-us-restrictions-we-arent-going-anywhere-2024-04-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[TikTok 首席执行官周三表示，该社交媒体公司预计将赢得一项法律挑战，以阻止总统乔·拜登签署的立法，他表示该法案将禁止 1.7 亿美国人使用其受欢迎的短视频应用程序。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktok-ceo-expects-defeat-us-restrictions-we-arent-going-anywhere-2024-04-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 15:23:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
